main event: A witness observed a UFO with multiple lights moving in a V-shape over Baton Rouge, Louisiana on June 27, 1966.
interesting points: The object was described as having a bluish glow and multicolored lights that flashed on and off., The object moved silently at variable speeds, making it difficult to describe., The sighting lasted for approximately 5-10 minutes before the object vanished into the distance., The witness was able to observe the object clearly with binoculars, which enhanced their view., No other reports were found in the area despite the proximity to an airport.
location: Baton Rouge, East Baton Rouge Parish, USA
witness description: An 18-year-old male who was in his backyard at the time of the sighting.
